  <itemBody>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h4>A collector has many viking items. Among other things, she has a viking axe. You really want to borrow the axe for the exhibition. You have written 4 versions of an e-mail to her. You have to decide how the collector will feel about every mail. </h4>
        <h6>You have to pick the feeling that fits every mail best. <br/>
Lastly, pick which mail you think would be the worst to send.</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <matchInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" maxAssociations="0" minAssociations="0">
          <prompt/>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="mail1" fixed="true" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">Mail 1:<br/>
Hi. Rune hill's historic museum are currently making an exhibition about the viking age for school children. We really want to borrow your axe for the exhibition. Then you will have the chance to share your interest for the viking age with a lot of young people.  </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="mail2" fixed="true" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">Mail 2:
<div>Hi. We have to borrow your viking helmet, can we come and get it sometime?</div></simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="mail3" fixed="true" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">
              <div>Mail 3:</div>
              <div>Hi. We want to borrow your viking helmet for one of our exhibitions. We hope that you will lend it to us voluntarily, or we will call our lawyers and find an argument to support that you as a private collector needs to lend items to national museums, when they ask you. </div>
              <div> </div>
            </simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="mail4" fixed="true" showHide="show" matchMax="1" matchMin="0">Mail 4:
<div>Hi. Rune hill's historic museum is very happy that you, with your big knowledge about the viking age, have collected valuable items from the north. We hope that you will share your knowledge with the local school children by lending us your viking helmet.</div></simpleAssociableChoice>
          </simpleMatchSet>
          <simpleMatchSet>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="proud" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Proud</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="happy" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Happy</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="annoyed" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Annoyed</simpleAssociableChoice>
            <simpleAssociableChoice identifier="angry" fixed="false" showHide="show" matchMax="0" matchMin="0">Angry</simpleAssociableChoice>
